{"tid":1973427,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9月21日屯門大會堂侮辱國旗案 判處鄧手足240小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-04-15T07:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:28:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c16fd1891cedd8b67c1aecdc9ee3121c13b9c043","tid":1973427,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"#屯門裁判法院第一庭 #0921屯門<br />\n#張潔宜署理主任裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤鄧(21) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：侮辱國旗<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2019年9月21日15:30，有康文署職員發現有人在屯門大會堂外平台扯下國旗，當中被告連同其他人撕開國旗，並以火槍及紙巾點燃國旗、踐踏國旗<br />\n<br />\n判詞：<br />\n考慮被告同意案情並坦白認罪，承諾不會再犯，無刑事定罪記錄。老闆及前中學老師都在求情信中表示被告勤奮好學、盡責，是一名好員工，好學生<br />\n<br />\n相信被告一時衝動犯下本案，接納感化官建議，判處240小時社會服務令，希望被告能深切反省<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F4190&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQFDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=c6ebc37f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4190</a>"},{"pid":"d2eb21696755900684bee4b9cc70c0e3ae3641f2","tid":1973427,"uid":309585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"律政司準備上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b978308436979e58ca9d86799ad952c7fac57f","tid":1973427,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【武漢肺炎】河南郟縣「二度封城」 3醫生被驗出是「隱形病人」致53人隔離<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973430</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8ec3ac10fba4632bb6b4074ba01f746d64174b49","tid":1973427,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"唔明典解認罪..."},{"pid":"6e4f005c94c6d16750b1de3cb35c0de7c35e43d0","tid":1973427,"uid":229275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec3ac10fba4632bb6b4074ba01f746d64174b49","tid":1973427,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislik